Module  : PM Reply Unquoted
Version : 1.0.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module changes the PM message reply link into a standard PM link,
so the forum message will not be quoted.


Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "pmreply_unquoted" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "PM Reply Unquoted".

